4136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:14:09.000Z","msg":"一齊行路返工好呀 又健康又有氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cc846af73e37ae92a4997a5cac87205e9dbc39","tid":1647783,"uid":321216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T18:23:08.000Z","msg":"已有暫定共識 行動post 18/10 有鑑於多位手足推極都推唔起 為免第一次活動太柒 試水溫行動將改於25/10 舉行<br />\n路線方面<br />\n只有港島東路線有更改<br />\n由炮台山站連儂牆行至太古坊(即鰂魚涌）<br />\n<br />\n稍後會補上行動更新post 請大家盡情對外推<br />\n25/10 和你返工 正式開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d205352b312273736bb15e09d2b3c643610d91b7","tid":1647783,"uid":321216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"推新post <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行動post 香港人！番工！1025和你返工<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1654514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1654514</a>"}]}